articles.description: Zach Braxton scored a career-high 25 points and tied a career high with 13 rebounds and Weber State beat Northern Colorado 71-66 in overtime on Saturday night.
articles.headline: Braxton, Harding lift Weber St. past N. Colorado 71-66 in OT

articles.description: Donte Clark scored 26 points with nine rebounds and five assists and Texas Southern beat Jackson State 86-75 on Saturday night.
articles.headline: Clark with 26 leads Texas Southern past Jackson State 86-75

articles.description: David Collette scored 18 points on 9-of-10 shooting in a dominant performance around the paint and led Utah to a 77-43 win over California on Saturday night.
articles.headline: Utah dominates California for 77-43 win

articles.description: Rui Hachimura scored 23 points and No. 12 Gonzaga kept the ball out of Jock Landale's hands to end the nation's longest active winning streak at 19 games with a 78-65 victory over No. 11 Saint Mary's on Saturday night.
articles.headline: Gonzaga snaps Saint Mary's 19-game win streak, 78-65

images.caption: Gonzaga head coach Mark Few credits his team for following direction and dominating offensively tonight to stay well-ahead of St. Mary's throughout the game.

videos.description: Terence Davis hits a 3-pointer off the assist from Bruce Stevens that gives Ole Miss an early lead against Alabama.
videos.headline: Davis drills corner 3

videos.description: Donta Hall gets the putback dunk off of the Avery Johnson Jr. missed 3-point attempt.
videos.headline: Tide's Hall puts back Johnson miss

videos.description: Collin Sexton knocks down a 3-pointer that ties Alabama with Ole Miss.
videos.headline: Sexton evens the score with 3

videos.description: Deandre Burnett drives and hits tough layup while drawing the foul for the Rebels.
videos.headline: Ole Miss' Burnett hits acrobatic layup

videos.description: Braxton Key makes a fast-break layup after a loose ball bounces in favor of the Crimson Tide.
videos.headline: Tide rolls with loose ball to set up Key layup

videos.description: Marcanvis Hymon cleans up the Deontae Shuler miss by throwing it down for Ole Miss.

videos.description: Markel Crawford throws down a fast-break dunk after jumping in front of the Alabama inbounds pass.
videos.headline: Crawford slams it home after stealing inbounds pass

videos.headline: Ole Miss bounces back to beat Bama 78-66
